743
00:55:25,720 --> 00:55:28,052
And with the passing
of every cosmic minute...

744
00:55:28,256 --> 00:55:30,315
...each minute 30,000 years long...

745
00:55:30,524 --> 00:55:32,856
...we began the arduous journey
