the universe that made us...

775
00:57:33,014 --> 00:57:36,245
...or we can squander
our 15 billion-year heritage...

776
00:57:36,450 --> 00:57:39,385
...in meaningless self-destruction.

777
00:57:40,621 --> 00:57:43,818
What happens in the first second
of the next cosmic year...

778
00:57:44,025 --> 00:57:47,188
...depends on what we do,
here and now...

779
00:57:47,395 --> 00:57:49,192
...with our intelligence...

780
00:57:49,397 --> 00:57:52,423
...and our knowledge of the cosmos.

